one of my fears that older people would be against me 
disappeared today as i met a lot of older people who said they 
were willing to back me he said 
the communist mongolian peoples revolutionary party which has 
ruled this central asian nation for seven decades clearly regarded 
district 12 as a safe place for ochirbat to run 
it is one of several bleak impoverished shantytowns on the 
fringes of ulan bator many of its 5300 registered voters have 
come recently from the countryside where communists are strongest 
and where there is little news of the revolution that has swept 
other soviet bloc nations 
neither candidate is from the district residency is not a 
legal requirement 
ochirbat may have expected that the residents could not resist 
the chance to have the ruling party chief as their hural delegate 
the party chairman a whitehaired dignifiedlooking man took 
office in march after popular demonstrations swept the incumbent of 
six years from power his past posts include head of the party 
ideology department president of the partycontrolled trade union 
and deputy chief of the party organization department 
