disastertype stresses on the central and interstate 280 freeways 
two weeks ago officials said the freeways which carry 250000 
vehicles a day would reopen in october 
the freeways resemble the cypress freeway that collapsed in 
oakland during the oct 17 earthquake the quake measured 71 on 
the richter scale killed 67 people and caused an estimated 7 
billion in damage the new freeways are expected to withstand a 
quake registering 82 on the richter scale 
