statebystate performance reports over objections from the white 
house 
thirtytwo states test elementary pupils statewide with the 
most popular tests being the california achievement test the 
stanford achievement test the metropolitan achievement test the 
science research associates test the comprehensive test of basic 
skills and the iowa test of basic skills 
the other 18 states allow local officials to pick the tests 
given to students in their district 
the national council of teachers of english has said repeatedly 
that standardized testing distorts and debases the language arts 
