indictments dismissed the high court refused to dismiss the 
indictments but it did declare unconstitutional a portion of the 
state laws definition of sexual conduct 
the case was among dozens souters office argued before the 
state court while he was attorney general in 197778 collectively 
they show he supported positions much like the tough lawandorder 
approach he later took as a state judge 
