purely sexual bond still his motive for engaging in a 
professionally and personally dangerous affair is fuzzy 
scacchi a european beauty is seductive and hungry as caroline 
she can be an ice queen but has a gentler side as when she coaxes 
an abused child into testifying against his mother 
as rustys wife barbara bonnie bedelia radiates compassion 
frustration love and fear it is one her strongest performances 
