for gay causes called it a very historic day because it will 
stop discrimination against people with aids and hiv infection 
the disabilities bill includes sanctions for those who 
discriminate in hiring it allows victims of employment 
discrimination to seek back pay reinstatement and attorneys fees 
however the law exempts businesses with fewer than 15 employees 
from the hiring provisions 
to businesses worried about the new mandates bush called the 
disabled a tremendous pool of potential workers who will 
bring to jobs diversity loyalty proven low turnover rate and only 
one request the chance to prove themselves 
sen bob dole rkan who lost use of his right arm in world 
war ii said the law was a giant step forward 
it will be some burden on business dole said but its 
going to make it much easier for americas disabled 
