waldheims wartime activities have been the subject of intense 
scrutiny since the revelations about his past 
an international commission of historians in 1987 did not 
confirm allegations that waldheim was personally guilty of war 
crimes but stated that he was in close proximity to wartime 
atrocities 
waldheim has persistently denied any wrongdoing 
