the strong turnout was reflected in 
clayton williams broad grin 
it was 9 am on a weekday morning and more than 150 people 
were gathered on the treeshaded lawn of the cumberland 
presbyterian church to meet williams the republican candidate for 
governor 
that he said is great 
its the biggest gathering for a republican candidate ever 
