im a farmer im a rancher i grew up in a small town 
smalltown values oldfashioned values are still the horse i 
believe is the one to ride he said 
i probably more truly represent what texans think they need 
and what they want in a governor 
the texas governors office is one of the top prizes of the 1990 
elections texas stands to pick up three or four us house seats 
