with a carefully prepared counter to litmus testing 
i do not believe that as a nominee i can tell you how i 
might vote on a particular issue which may come before the court 
or endorse or criticize specific supreme court decisions presenting 
issues which may well come before the court again to do so would 
mean i have prejudged the matter 
