limiting the deductability of state and local income taxes on 
federal tax returns a gop bargainer said today such deductions 
would be limited to no more than 10000 said the negotiator who 
asked not to be identified 
the package does not include two other types of taxes on 
tobacco and on luxury items such as jewelry that the negotiators 
have been considering said the official 
