mermaid and theatrical release of pretty woman hollywoods 
highestgrossing film this year 
next quarters results should get a boost from dick tracy 
which was released in late june and arachnophobia the killer 
spider thriller from disneys new hollywood pictures studio which 
wells has predicted will be one of the summers biggest smashes 
</TEXT>
