year ago 
for the years first half the nations fourthlargest oil 
company said net income totaled 112 billion or 316 a share up 
56 percent from 717 million or 209 a share in the 1989 first 
half revenue rose 15 percent to 183 billion from 159 billion 
on higher sales volumes for crude oil natural gas and petroleum 
products particularly in the first quarter 
